df = pd.read_csv('ConstructionTimeSeriesDataV2.csv')
print(df)
xx = list(df['Public Construction'])
yy = defaultdict(list)
zz = []
opc = []
for i in xx:
    yy[xx.index(i)%12].append(i)
for i in yy.values():
    zz.append(i)
for i in zz:
    for j in i:
        opc.append(j)
df['Ordered Public Construction'] = opc
xx = list(df['Private Construction'])
yy = defaultdict(list)
zz = []

for i in xx:
    yy[xx.index(i)%12].append(i)
for i in yy.values():
    zz.append(i)
for i in zz:
    for j in i:
        opc.append(j)
df['Ordered Private Construction'] = opc

In [275]:
slope, intercept, r_value, p_value, std_err = stats.linregress(df.index, df['Public Construction'])
tmp = []
for i in range(len(df['Ordered Public Construction'])):
    tmp.append(float(intercept) + i * slope)

df['regress'] = tmp
df['R1Public'] = df['Ordered Public Construction'] - df['regress']
df.style.format({
    'Ordered Public Construction': '{:,.0f}'.format, 
    'regress': '{:,.0f}'.format, 
    'R1Public': '{:,.0f}'.format
})

plot each annual pattern simultaneously to view seasonal trends

In [281]:
avg = []
for i in range(len(dfYear.index)):
    avg.append(dfYear.iloc[i].mean())

dfYear = pd.concat([dfYear, pd.DataFrame({'avg': avg})], axis=1)
fig, ax = plt.subplots()
for col in dfYear.columns.values:
    if col == 'avg':
        ax.plot(dfYear[col], c='r')
    else:
        ax.plot(dfYear[col], c='k')

In [282]:
df['SPublic'] = np.NaN
df['R2Public'] = np.NaN
df['Composite'] = np.NaN
df['R2ErrorPublic'] = np.NaN
S = avg
for i in df.index:
    df.loc[i, 'SPublic'] = S[i%period]
    df.loc[i, 'R2Public'] = df.loc[i, 'R1Public'] - df.loc[i, 'SPublic']
    df.loc[i, 'Composite'] = df.loc[i, 'regress'] + df.loc[i, 'SPublic']
    df.loc[i, 'R2ErrorPublic'] = 100*df.loc[i, 'R2Public'] / df.loc[i,  'Ordered Public Construction']
df.style.format({
    'Ordered Public Construction': '{:,.0f}'.format, 
    'regress': '{:,.0f}'.format, 
    'R1Public': '{:,.0f}'.format,
    'SPublic': '{:,.0f}'.format, 
    'R2Public': '{:,.0f}'.format,
    'Composite': '{:,.0f}'.format, 
    'R2ErrorPublic': '{:,.2f}'.format,
})

df['SPriv'] = np.NaN
df['R2Priv'] = np.NaN
df['CompositePriv'] = np.NaN
df['R2ErrorPriv'] = np.NaN
S = avg
for i in df.index:
    df.loc[i, 'SPriv'] = S[i%period]
    df.loc[i, 'R2Priv'] = df.loc[i, 'R1Priv'] - df.loc[i, 'SPriv']
    df.loc[i, 'CompositePriv'] = df.loc[i, 'MovAvg'] + df.loc[i, 'SPriv']
    df.loc[i, 'R2ErrorPriv'] = 100*df.loc[i, 'R2Priv'] / df.loc[i,  'Ordered Private Construction']

for i in df['R2Priv']:
    squerrpriv.append(i*i)
df['SqErrPriv'] = squerrpriv
cumsquerrpriv = [np.NaN]*12
for i in range(12, len(squerrpriv) - 12):
    cumsquerrpriv.append(sum(squerrpriv[12:i+1]))
for i in range(12):
    cumsquerrpriv.append(np.NaN)
df['CumSqErrPriv'] = cumsquerrpriv
